<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?><song><title>msẖwạr ʿmry</title>
<lyrics>[V1]
 1- msẖwạr ʿmry ạlly fạt wạlly qḍyth fy ậhạt
 nsyth klh lmạ qạblt ạlly ʿny mạt
 smʿth lmạ ndạny bṣrkẖẗ mn ʿly̱ ạlṣlyb
 wsẖfth whw mkạny bytạ̉lm fy ạllhyb
 2- msẖwạr ʿmry ạlly kạn mlyạn bạldmwʿ
 nsyth klh lmạ qạblt rby yswʿ
 smʿth lmạ ndạny sẖʿrt bṣwt ʿjyb
 wʿrft ạ̹nh ạsẖtrạny bdmh ạ̉ʿẓm ḥbyb
 3- msẖwạr ʿmry trkth wdʿth bkl mạ fyh
 nsyth klh lmạ slmt ʿmry fy ạ̹ydyh
 smʿth lmạ ndạny bnfsh rb ạlḥyạẗ
 bạlrwḥ hw mlạny whdạny ṭwq ạlnjạẗ</lyrics>
<author>kạml bqṭr, bytr jmạl</author>
